CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 1, 1952, pg. 22, reads: "Courier Analyst Returns Home - When the Eisenhower Special Train arrived at Pennsylvania Station Monday night... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Crowd gathered around President Dwight D. Eisenhower in Pennsylvania Station, Downtown
